strings.Value: "Did you hear that, boys and girls? A few more days — and we're on a diet. We're running out of food!"
"Our chief doesn't care about us — and soon we'll be walking around hungry..."
"A hungry traveler is a traveler in peril. If I'm not well-fed, I won't be able to solve all the problems the world keeps dumping on us!"
"If we run out of meals — I can always just eat you. Ah ha ha ha hah!"
"If you're hungry, just tell me. I'll share whatever I have."
"Why be sad, friend? The spirit is stronger than the flesh. You of all people must know this, Regongar."
How could you go hungry in a land covered with lush greenery?"
